23
00:00:56.655 --> 00:00:59.620
This life here is gonna work.
isn't it?

24
00:00:59.724 --> 00:01:01.551
We'll make it work.

25
00:01:02.413 --> 00:01:04.344
♪

26
00:01:10.379 --> 00:01:12.517
