called Rio Paloma.

44
00:02:22.241 --> 00:02:23.931
About an hour from the border.

45
00:02:24.793 --> 00:02:26.034
How much land?

46
00:02:26.896 --> 00:02:28.241
Five thousand acres.

47
00:02:28.310 --> 00:02:29.448
Black Angus.

48
00:02:29.517 --> 00:02:31.137
175 head on it.

49
00:02:31.206 --> 00:02:32.827
