50
00:02:32.896 --> 00:02:34.655
About every nickel we got.

51
00:02:36.896 --> 00:02:39.620
Cheaper than rebuilding here.
that's for sure.

52
00:02:39.689 --> 00:02:41.931
♪ low. somber music ♪

53
00:02:44.551 --> 00:02:46.793
Will it give us
the life we want. baby?

54
00:02:46.862 --> 00:02:48.620
In success. yeah.

55
00:02:50.724 --> 00:02:52.931
- Want to take a ride?
- I don't want

56
00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:54.827
to spend another night here.

57
00:03:01.448 --> 00:03:04.551
