just as it is.

67
00:03:36.103 --> 00:03:40.793
The prospect of someday
feeding folks with our beef...

68
00:03:41.724 --> 00:03:44.827
...that was
Billy's dying pride and joy.

69
00:03:45.931 --> 00:03:49.931
Rip. I'm trusting that you
will fulfill that prospect.

70
00:03:50.758 --> 00:03:52.172
That's all that matters to me.

71
00:03:53.758 --> 00:03:56.551
Because he was
all that mattered.

72
00:03:56.620 --> 00:03:58.448
